<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Nicl<ex>as</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Griesz, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex>s,</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir in
                                <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brief hören
                            <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> und er spricht, er wöll ew
                                <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
                        darauf tün. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
                        Bonifacii.</ab>
